Batman_-_Bruce_Wayne_-_Murderer_(2014)_(digital-Empire) 


After being found with the dead body of Vesper Fairchild in his arms, Bruce Wayne is arrested for murder. Looking to prove Bruce's innocence, Nightwing, Robin, and Batgirl quickly begin an investigation to discover the true killer. But as the mystery unfolds, evidence of Bruce's guilt mounts and even his closest allies are beginning to question their mentor's innocence. Tired of portraying himself as someone he is not and further embracing the freedom of his masked identity, Bruce decides to lay his millionaire playboy alter ego to rest and live life only as the Batman.
